---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen bg-brand-black text-brand-white flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-40" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?q=80&w=1974');"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif leading-tight">
          Go Beyond the Session.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-sans mt-6 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Transform your framework into a 24/7 AI Integration Partner, and empower your clients to live the work you teach.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-brand-white text-brand-black font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-wider py-4 px-8 hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-all duration-300 rounded-md">
          Book a Discovery Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-brand-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif leading-tight text-brand-black">
          Transformation doesn't happen on a schedule.
        </h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-lg mt-6 leading-relaxed text-brand-black/80">
          Your sessions are powerful. Your workshops create breakthroughs. But the real work—the messy, courageous work of integration—happens at 10 PM on a Tuesday, or in the five minutes before a high-stakes meeting. It's in these moments your clients need you most.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528543606781-2f6e6857f318?q=80&w=1965" alt="A person walking on a beach" class="rounded-lg w-full h-auto object-cover">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pillars Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-brand-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif leading-tight text-brand-black">
                Give them a space to step into.
            </h2>
            <p class="font-sans text-lg mt-4 leading-relaxed text-brand-black/80">
                Introducing the AI Integration Partner by Storysmith.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold">Embody the Learnings</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-black/70">Move from intellectually understanding a framework to viscerally knowing it through guided, daily practice.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold">Build Real Confidence</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-black/70">Safely rehearse difficult conversations and high-stakes scenarios until they feel unstoppable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2">
                <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold">Find In-the-Moment Clarity</h3>
                <p class="text-brand-black/70">Access your guidance 24/7, turning moments of doubt into opportunities for growth.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Testimonial Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center max-w-4xl">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-brand-black">From an Hour a Week to an "Always-On" Ally</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif italic my-10">
            "It's the ultimate bridge between sessions. My clients now have a confidential space to practice my frameworks and get support the moment they need it. The level of integration and the results they're achieving are beyond anything I thought possible."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <img src="/path/to/emma-headshot.png" alt="Emma Kirkman" class="h-16 w-16 rounded-full object-cover">
            <div>
                <p class="font-sans font-bold">Emma Kirkman</p>
                <p class="font-sans text-sm text-brand-black/60">Founder, Scaled Ambition</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-brand-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-brand-black">We build the engine. You provide the genius.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-16">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1588196749107-45b1b30811e5?q=80&w=2070" alt="People brainstorming on a whiteboard" class="rounded-lg">
            <div><h3 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-4">1. The Blueprint</h3><p class="font-sans text-lg text-brand-black/80">We start with a deep immersion into your unique methodology. We don't just read your content; we learn your philosophy to design an AI that is a true extension of you.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="md:order-2"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555066931-4365d1469c88?q=80&w=2070" alt="Hands coding on a laptop" class="rounded-lg"></div>
            <div class="md:order-1"><h3 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-4">2. The Build</h3><p class="font-sans text-lg text-brand-black/80">Our team builds your bespoke AI Integration Partner. It's a white-glove process where we handle all the technology, allowing you to focus on your expertise.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521737604893-d14cc237f11d?q=80&w=2084" alt="Team members looking at a laptop" class="rounded-lg">
            <div><h3 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-4">3. The Handover</h3><p class="font-sans text-lg text-brand-black/80">We deliver a beautifully branded, ready-to-use platform for your clients. It's your world, your genius—activated.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-brand-black mb-6">Technology Built on Trust.</h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-lg mb-12 text-brand-black/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto">In a world of extractive tech, we choose to build differently. Storysmith is a values-led company, and every integration partner we build is grounded in our public Foundation Charter—a sacred commitment to:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold">Absolute Data Sovereignty</h3><p class="text-brand-black/70">Your clients' stories are sacred and belong only to them. Period.</p></div>
        <div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold">Ethical AI</h3><p class="text-brand-black/70">We build tools that empower human agency and connection, not diminish them.</p></div>
        <div class="space-y-2"><h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold">Purposeful Partnership</h3><p class="text-brand-black/70">Your success is our success. We are deeply invested in amplifying the work of those who create positive change.</p></div>
      </div>
      <a href="/philosophy" class="inline-block mt-12 border border-brand-black text-brand-black font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-wider py-3 px-8 hover:bg-brand-black hover:text-brand-white transition-colors rounded-md">Read Our Foundation Charter</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA Section -->
  <section class="relative py-32 md:py-48 bg-brand-black text-brand-white flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-40" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506794778202-cad84cf45f1d?q=80&w=1974');"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto relative z-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif leading-tight">Ready to bridge the integration gap?</h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-xl my-8 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">Schedule a complimentary, 20-minute discovery call to explore how an AI Integration Partner can create deeper transformation for your clients and unlock new levels of impact for your business.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-brand-white text-brand-black font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-wider py-4 px-8 hover:bg-opacity-90 transition-colors rounded-md">
          Book Your Discovery Call
        </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>